CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

April 6, 2011

[Cite as 04/06/2011 Case Announcements, 2011-Ohio-1618.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2010-0115. Willis Day Warehousing Co. v. Wood Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, Nos. 2006-M-1794 and 2007-M-868. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Lundberg Stratton, Lanzinger, Cupp, and McGee Brown, JJ., concur. Pfeifer and O’Donnell, JJ., dissent.
